<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.5.3">
<l>māṉāya meṉṉōkki vāṇeṭuṅkaṇ ṇīrmalkum vaḷaiyuñ cōrum</l>
<l>tēṉāya naṟuntuḻāya laṅkaliṉti ṟampēci yuṟaṅkāḷ kāṇmiṉ</l>
<l>kāṉāyaṉ kaṭimaṉaiyil tayiruṇṭu neyparuka nantaṉ peṟṟa</l>
<l>vāṉāya ṉeṉmakaḷaic ceytaṉaka ḷammaṉaimī raṟiki lēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Her] long lance[-like] eyes, glancing softly as a deer’s, well with tears;</l>
<l rend="indent">her bangles slip.</l>
<l>She does not sleep, reciting of the qualities of the tulasī garland,</l>
<l rend="indent">fragrant as nectar. [Just] look!</l>
<l>The herder boy whom Nanda got, so that he could enjoy ghee,</l>
<l rend="indent">having eaten curds in the guarded houses of the herders of the woodlands,</l>
<l>Ladies, I cannot understand what [he] did to my daughter!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
